Close the governor valve, cut the
propulsion, we gotta isolate the boiler.

555
00:49:53,641 --> 00:49:56,019
We gotta conserve
everything she's got left.

556
00:49:56,227 --> 00:50:00,351
I keep tellin' ya...
this boat's just bad luck.

557
00:50:00,401 --> 00:50:04,445
It's got nothing...
to do... with luck.

558
00:50:36,773 --> 00:50:41,484
Station Chatham,
this is the CG-36-500, do you copy?

559
00:50:41,571 --> 00:50:45,656
<i>This is Station Chatham, 36-500,
what is your location. Over.

560
00:50:45,867 --> 00:50:50,189
<i>Station Chatham, we are...
we are now passing Morris Island,

561
00:50:51,039 --> 00:50:54,096
heading down the channel
towards Chatham bar. Over.

562
00:50:54,151 --> 00:50:57,297
