00:53:52,020 --> 00:53:57,335
10 to 12 miles east of Monomoy
<i>Point, movin' south. Over.

605
00:53:58,628 --> 00:54:03,842
Station Chatham, this
is the 500... copy that.

606
00:54:15,439 --> 00:54:18,551
I hear what everyone's sayin'.

607
00:54:19,629 --> 00:54:21,520
You don't know
what you're doing.

608
00:54:22,739 --> 00:54:24,242
Excuse me?

609
00:54:24,574 --> 00:54:27,807
Maybe... maybe it's because
you're not from here.

610
00:54:27,857 --> 00:54:28,802
You don't know what
it's like out there.

611
00:54:28,928 --> 00:54:32,933
What the hell would you know
what it's like out there, Miss? Hmm?

612
00:54:34,002 --> 00:54:35,753
Please just call them back.

613
00:54:35,920 --> 00:54:39,132
What do you think it's gonna be like
being married to a Coast<i> Guard man?

