00:54:48,059 --> 00:54:53,388
- Please call them back.
- Get out of here! Get outta my station!

618
00:54:53,438 --> 00:54:56,525
<i>- And go home to where you belong, Miss.</i>
- Please call them back.

619
00:54:56,652 --> 00:54:58,479
Get out my station!

