<i>So I'm gonna wait for
a low</i> and then we go.

634
00:59:14,390 --> 00:59:16,248
We got faith in you, Skip.

635
00:59:16,648 --> 00:59:20,244
<i>Anytime you're ready,
you just go, Bernie, all right?

